The '''Crimson Casino''' was a casino and a bar located on [[The Wheel/Legends|The ''Wheel'']].

==History==
The Crimson Casino was located on the upper level of [[The Wheel/Legends|The ''Wheel'']], and only the extremely wealthy were allowed in. When [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]], [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]], [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] and [[Chewbacca/Legends|Chewbacca]] arrived on The Wheel shortly after the [[Battle of Yavin/Legends|Battle of Yavin]], they agreed to meet in this casino, although only Chewbacca actually made it because all the others were captured by [[Wheel Security Force]]. However, Chewbacca hadn't paid his registration fee and got into a fight with a [[Mandallian Giant]].

